{"tid":723170,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Gin Lee海豚音爆發 後台絕密片段","createTime":"2018-06-30T07:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T06:10:59.000Z","uid":160977,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec19c2d70465fc4f9a368f63077ab9f92e7daaf","tid":723170,"uid":160977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"演唱會舞台設計主要採用了一大片綠草，營造大自然的感覺，而且配合主題「花」，第一部分的黎明破曉時分，Gin Lee披上一襲長達十呎的特製斗篷從升降台出場，以《光環》、《隨風而來隨風而去》揭開序幕。脫去斗篷，裏面是黃色露肩百l褶大傘裙，原來內有乾坤，最後一層是粉紅透視露背長裙，三套衣服一層一層演變，非常有心思。<br />\n<br />\nGin Lee家鄉是馬來西亞，她以馬拉話唱出了地道歌曲《Getaren Jiwa》，Gin Lee更分享隻身來港時的種種艱辛，她說：「試過凌晨兩點肚痛，不知可以打給誰？每逢過節都特別寂寞，又試過窮到無錢交租。不過，明日又是新的開始，當大家覺得難受挫敗可以聽吓我的歌。」Gin Lee也分享了一句自己的格言：「It&rsquo;s all about your mind!」<br />\n雖然Gin Lee的家人居住在馬來西亞，但對Gin Lee非常支持，出身於音樂世家的她，自小在音樂環境下長大，今次首踏紅館，姊夫負責彈低音結他，爸爸負責打鼓，Gin Lee分別與父母、姊姊唱出《給我一個吻》、《My Way》和《Hey Jude》，一家人一開口，聲線非常合拍，場面溫馨之餘亦有驚喜，也盡顯最強音樂世家的音樂基因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2tFGXR9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tFGXR9&d=q37Okwz3dMy7n%2BC1cFV2dwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7be91f2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2tFGXR9</a>"},{"pid":"475923cb6cf418787d6b8c11a5e7ad8501d4785c","tid":723170,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c115aebbcb043107fb91c84337ef144afd4a155","tid":723170,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"d衫唔夠性感"},{"pid":"0cf6f0a71202e1f46fda4afdaf918e67c82a4453","tid":723170,"uid":6604,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"唱歌正過雞容勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6060b8bab2f76c8cfc7701527607dd877fdc841a","tid":723170,"uid":143206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0cf6f0a71202e1f46fda4afdaf918e67c82a4453","tid":723170,"uid":6604,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"唱歌正過雞容勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab6f4d37bc089388d7dc2fb6681f55c86687720","tid":723170,"uid":81569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"如果佢肯露肉賣波陪老闆<br />\n應該做左香港一姐"},{"pid":"25703c132b681682087b054624248769244ed065","tid":723170,"uid":143206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ab6f4d37bc089388d7dc2fb6681f55c86687720","tid":723170,"uid":81569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"如果佢肯露肉賣波陪老闆<br />\n應該做左香港一姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}